Ira D. HallBorn: c. 1945Gender: MaleRace or Ethnicity: BlackOccupation: BusinessNationality: United StatesExecutive summary: Utendahl Capital Management    University: BS EE, Stanford University    University: MBA, Stanford University    Administrator: Dean's Advisory Council, Stanford University Graduate School of Business    Utendahl Capital Management Senior Advisor (2005-)
