    Texaco GM Alliance Management (1998-99)
    IBM (13 years)
    L. F. Rothschild, Unterberg, Towbin Senior VP (past)
    Member of the Board of Ameriprise Financial (2005-)
    Member of the Board of Oce Imagistics (2001-)
    Member of the Board of Pepsi Beverages Company (2003-)
    Member of the Board of Praxair (2004-)
    Member of the Board of Reynolds and Reynolds (2002-?)
    Member of the Board of Southern New England Telecommunications (1995-?)
    Member of the Board of TECO Energy (2001-04)
    Executive Leadership Council Chairman (past)    Jackie Robinson Foundation Board of Directors    Obama for America 




