Set Up an Account




 





Call your financial professional to open an account with American Funds. Don’t have a financial advisor? We can help you find one.



 
 The Value of a Financial Professional Why all investors can benefit from the experience and guidance of a financial advisor. 
 










Roll Over an Account




 





Your financial professional can help you open a rollover IRA with us. 
American Funds Rollover Specialists are also available at (800) 421-9923 from 8:00 a.m. to 7:00 p.m., Monday through Friday, to answer any questions you may have about the rollover process.



 
 








