$117,000 or less — full contribution 
$117,000–$131,999 — partial contribution 
$132,000 or more — not eligible 

Joint filers with MAGI of:

$184,000 or less — full contribution 
$184,000 –$193,999 — partial contribution 
$194,000 or more — not eligible 

Married, filing separately with MAGI of:

$0–$9,999 — partial contribution
$10,000 or more — not eligible 

For 2017:

 Single filers with MAGI of:

$118,000 or less — full contribution
$118,000–$132,999 — partial contribution
$133,000 or more — not eligible

Joint filers with MAGI of:

$186,000 or less — full contribution
